cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a novel end-to-end, non-intrusive speech quality evaluation model based on bidirectional long short-term memory. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as Speech and Audio Processing (cs.SD), Computation and Language (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Signal Processing (cs.SI). However, since the focus of the paper is on speech quality assessment, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category.
